lightroot is a small project for tracking cells in growing root tips.
*********************************************************************
To use with your data either load the pipeline notebook or run: python __main__.py [your data folder]

Files in the data folder must follow a format such as Frame0001.tif. A custom format can be specified in the settings file

Better installation process and notes to follow: 
In short, using a distribution such as anaconda and pip installing tqdm for the progress bar should do it.
